tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE play_counts (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    song_id INT,
    play_count INT,
    last_played TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    age INT,
    gender TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE recommendations (
    recommendation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    song_id INT,
    recommendation_score FLOAT,
    recommendation_date TIMESTAMP
);
